<item>
            <title>[LU-10064] Publish ZFS userspace rpms on lustre download site</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10064</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Before Lustre 2.10.1 GA IML has been using Lustre Jenkins builds. These builds include zfs rpms that IML uses.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the Lustre download site, we don&apos;t have these same rpms in tow, so installing with ZFS fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a request to add those same zfs rpms to the download site, or failing that, someone to sign off that they are ok with us shipping IML 4.0 against a lustre jenkins URL.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="48567">LU-10064</key>
            <summary>Publish ZFS userspace rpms on lustre download site</summary>
